NAME
    Date::Leapyear - Is a particular year a leap year?

SYNOPSIS
      use Date::Leapyear;
      if ( isleap(1945) ) {
        ...
      }

DESCRIPTION
    Date::Leapyear exports one function - isleap - which returns 1 or 0 if a
    year is leap, or not, respectively.

isleap
        $true = isleap( 2004 );

    Returns 1 in a leap year, 0 otherwise.

